Package: koreader-remote-turner
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), liblzma5 (>= 5.2), libpango-1.0-0 (>= 1.50), libcairo2 (>= 1.16), libgdk-pixbuf2.0-0 (>= 2.42)
Maintainer: Shin Curry <shin@curry.jp>
Homepage: https://github.com/shin-curry/koreader-remote-turner
Description: Remote control KOReader via volume buttons
 Turn pages forward/backward and send sleep commands to KOReader
 wirelessly through a WebSocket connection. Listen for hardware
 volume key presses on Android, iOS, Windows, macOS, and Linux.
